text:
Another doctor died yesterday in Leicester.He had been on ventilator since contracting COVID-19 from a patient but but passed away last night.We have now 3 confirmed deaths of doctors in last few days due to COVID-19
Mr Amged El’Hawrani
Mr Adil El Tayar
Dr Habib Zaidi
